---

<section id="cta" class="section sec-cta">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="cta-block">
      <div class="section-eyebrow"><span>06 — Kostenlos &amp; unverbindlich</span></div>
      <h2 class="cta-headline">Zeig uns deinen Betrieb. Wir machen dich schlagkräftiger als jedes Team ohne KI.</h2>
      <p class="cta-text">Standardlösung oder individuell gebaut — wir finden was für deinen Betrieb passt. 30 Minuten. Kostenlos. Ohne Versprechen die wir nicht halten.</p>

      <a href="https://calendly.com/onlinemaster711/new-meeting" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span>Jetzt kostenloses Gespräch buchen</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
      </a>

      <div class="cta-meta">
        <span>30 Minuten</span>
        <span>Ohne Verpflichtung</span>
        <span>Per Telefon-Call</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sec-cta {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--on-surface);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .sec-cta .section-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* CTA-Block = grüne Karte, zentriert in heller Sektion */
  .cta-block {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px 0 rgba(27, 28, 26, 0.12);
  }

  /* Section-Eyebrow — rote Linie davor */
  .sec-cta .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--primary-fixed);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .sec-cta .section-eyebrow::before {
    content: "";
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--secondary);
  }

  .cta-headline {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--primary-fixed);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  /* Button Primary */
  .sec-cta .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b80049 0%, #8c0037 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.125rem 2rem;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .sec-cta .btn-primary:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(184, 0, 73, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .sec-cta .btn-primary .arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
  }

  .sec-cta .btn-primary:hover .arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  /* CTA-Meta mit roten Dot-Separatoren */
  .cta-meta {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 3rem;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--primary-fixed);
  }

  .cta-meta span {
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-meta span + span::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: -1.5rem;
    top: 50%;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--secondary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .sec-cta { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .cta-block { padding: 2.5rem 1.75rem; }
    .cta-meta { gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .cta-meta span + span::before { left: -1rem; }
    .sec-cta .btn-primary { padding: 1rem 1.75rem; }
  }
</style>
